name: Unidentified_Human_(Namman_Cha)
content:
A male Human Force-sensitive engaged the Dark Jedi Namman Cha in lightsaber combat at some point during the Galactic Civil War. He wore a robe resembling that of the Jedi apparel and wielded a blue-bladed lightsaber in battle.
This character was depicted on the "Lightsaber Block" card of the Champions of the Force, the base set of the Star Wars Galaxies Trading Card Game, which was illustrated by artist Kieran Yanner. Since the time period of the game is set around 0 ABY-3 ABY, it is uncertain whether this character may be identified as a proper member of the Jedi Order.
